'''Slobodan Marshall''' (born 2004), better known by his stage name '''Slo Bo''', is an American rapper. He is the son of Air Force pilot and engineer [[Jake Marshall]]. 

==Early life==
Slobodan was born in 2004 to Jake Marshall and his wife, Zeljana Valhovic.

